Scope note (current state)
--------------------------
This repository is the Unreal Engine 5 code/logic project. The art it tracks
directly is limited to the project's own framework assets, all original and
CC BY 4.0: the Material Parameter Collection
(`Content/Materials/MPC_GTCGlobals.uasset`), the GameMode and HUD Blueprints
(`Content/Core/BP_GTCGameMode.uasset`, `Content/UI/WBP_GTCHud.uasset`), and the
Enhanced Input assets (`Content/Input/`). The bulk of the game art is NOT tracked
here: it lives in the private `Content/GTCaliberAssets/` Git LFS submodule under
its own third-party licenses (see docs/ASSET_HANDLING.md). Any new
project-authored art added under `Content/` is governed by this file (CC BY 4.0)
unless its own per-folder LICENSE says otherwise, and must carry a provenance row
in docs/ASSETS.md.

Vehicle meshes: the previously-referenced AI-generated (Tripo Studio) vehicle
meshes were removed before public release pending verification of
AI-generation redistribution rights. Licensed vehicle meshes (Fab / CC0 /
original) will be added later. The vehicle *logic* (ownership, condition,
health, chop-shop) is C++ and mesh-agnostic, and is unaffected.

